IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. REPORTE.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-I     PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.
01 WS-VENTA PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.
01 WS-TOTAL PIC 9(7) VALUE 0.
01 WS-DISP  PIC ZZZ,ZZ9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
    DISPLAY '== VENTAS =='.
    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > 3
        COMPUTE WS-VENTA = WS-I * 1000
        ADD WS-VENTA TO WS-TOTAL
        MOVE WS-VENTA TO WS-DISP
        DISPLAY '  ' WS-DISP
    END-PERFORM.
    MOVE WS-TOTAL TO WS-DISP.
    DISPLAY 'TOTAL:' WS-DISP.
    STOP RUN.
